text: Georges Ginesta (born July 8, 1942 in Saint-Raphaël, Var) is a member of the National Assembly of France. He represents the Var department, and is a member of the Union for a Popular Movement. ==References== Category:1942 births Category:Living people Category:People from Saint-Raphaël, Var Category:Union for a Popular Movement politicians Category:Deputies of the 12th National Assembly of the French Fifth Republic Category:Deputies of the 13th National Assembly of the French Fifth Republic Category:Deputies of the 14th National Assembly of the French Fifth Republic Category:Senators of Var (department)
